  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Enjoy the excellent continental buffet breakfast which includes a selection of delicious local products and boiled eggs. Additional items can be ordered (at an additional charge).</p>
<p>The lodge is just a short walk from the town centre which has a wide variety of bars and restaurants to enjoy.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
