  <description><![CDATA[<p>Look forward to a warm welcome at this small, traditional Bed &amp; Breakfast Swiss Lodge, offering good value, simple accommodation and a friendly atmosphere.</p>
<h2>Impressive views of the Eiger</h2>
<p>Most rooms are south-facing with a balcony and spectacular views of the Eiger. They're are located in either the main building or the close-by Crystal annexe building and are a comfortable base for an active holiday.</p>
<h2>Excellent location</h2>
<p>The Jungfrau Lodge is located just a four-minute walk from <a data-udi="umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da}" title="Grindelwald">Grindelwald</a> train station for easy access to the Jungfrau walking area, and two minutes' walk from the resort bus stop for the First and Männlichen lifts - it's easy to walk to them too</p>]]></description>
